<body>
    <h1>Eratosthenes's Measure of the Earth's Circumference</h1>
    <p>This visualization demonstrates Eratosthenes's method of measuring the Earth's circumference using the angles of shadows cast by the sun at different latitudes.</p>
    <div id="control-panel">
        <label for="slider-post-angle">Post angle</label>
        <input type="range" id="slider-post-angle" value="7" min="1" max="60" step="0.1">
        <span id="display-post-angle"></span>
        <label for="checkbox-zoom">Zoom</label>
