This code creates a basic HTML structure with a control panel and a canvas container. It uses the Three.js library to create a 3D scene and render it on the canvas. The scene includes a polyhedron that can be folded and unfolded using the slider. The folding state is updated dynamically based on the slider value. The view can be reset to its initial state using the reset button.

